ank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cagliari</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 30 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Creiamo assieme un sito web con WordPress, il mio metodo!&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/288305202/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 30 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Come gestire 100 siti WordPress da un solo pannello con ManageWP&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/288305202/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2022/09/meetup-di-settembre-2022/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Ti aspettiamo a WordCamp Italia 2022\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2022/09/ti-aspettiamo-a-wordcamp-italia-2022/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://it.